&lt;p&gt;Set and execute the social media strategy to grow reach, engagement, and community across core audience segments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop creative social campaigns around product launches, company announcements, and thought leadership themes tied to your content strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
